{"tid":2354013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"質疑被告鎖手銬面對三警如何拒捕  官拒納警證供 工人脫兩罪","createTime":"2021-01-05T07:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T13:11:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5b45b746cb843234c2bb52d64c1e724b3970e915","tid":2354013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:29:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/KVSQGPMMZ5BLRDG45VWJRMPS7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FKVSQGPMMZ5BLRDG45VWJRMPS7Y%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=b11547ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FKVSQGPMMZ5BLRDG45VWJRMPS7Y%2F&h=8a4dad1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/KVSQGPMMZ5BLRDG45VWJRMPS7Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n質疑被告鎖手銬面對三警如何拒捕 <br />\n官拒納警證供 工人脫兩罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vNKY9MFtFFamu11vOvILNKHguNU=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZIWMZ4XO2BELZDVWB2X3AU27C4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvNKY9MFtFFamu11vOvILNKHguNU%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZIWMZ4XO2BELZDVWB2X3AU27C4.jpg&h=e8dbe627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告陳卓傑昨獲裁定兩罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方前年9月22日在旺角警署對開驅散示威者時拘捕一名運輸工，指他藏有雷射筆及拒捕。案件昨裁決，裁判官質疑警員為何不在報案室搜身，反而在升降機大堂搜，且被告當時被鎖上手銬，單人匹馬面對三名警員仍拒捕的說法不合理；儘管不信被告稱雷射筆有工作用途，惟控方未能證明它是用來傷人，裁定被告兩罪名均不成立。<br />\n<br />\n被告陳卓傑（49歲）被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器及拒捕兩罪，指他當晚在港鐵太子站外管有雷射筆，及抗拒警員王立聰執行職務。被告曾質疑警方濫權，去年5月底入稟區院指控警方對他使用非法武力。<br />\n<br />\n負責拘捕及制服被告的警員王。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官施祖堯裁決時指王證供不合理，例如王在升降機大堂搜查被告，惟報案室非常接近，質疑為何王不帶被告到報案室，王亦同意在報案室搜查是更安全及較理想的地方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cuKhn2VLCvutHyLuLdhMdX7MfvQ=/1154x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BJCWGWSU5BAMTNJLXTMEOVOZLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcuKhn2VLCvutHyLuLdhMdX7MfvQ%3D%2F1154x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBJCWGWSU5BAMTNJLXTMEOVOZLY.jpg&h=bbc78cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員王立聰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方未證藏雷射筆傷人<br />\n<br />\n施官又指被告單人匹馬身處警署，被鎖上手銬，且被三名警員扣押，任何人都自知沒有機會能逃離警署，施官認為這些都屬證供關鍵之處，卻出現不合理的地方，不接納王的證供，裁定被告拒捕罪脫。<br />\n<br />\n被告自辯稱從事運輸及網台直播工作，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n施官又引述發現塗鴉的女警的證供，女警指持噴漆者穿啡色短褲，被告當時穿藍色牛仔褲，警方亦沒有在被告背囊搜出噴漆。施官指沒證據顯示現場有人群聚集或示威活動，路人可路過現場，附近亦有巴士上落乘客；被告雖有逃走，但沒證據顯示他跟警方作出對抗行為，控方未能證明他藏有雷射筆是用作傷人的唯一合理推論，裁定他在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪同樣不成立。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC2284/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u4YKus9AV13jXuqRKRtu4a5RP4I=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RV5JY5QGGBBDRPKM2LGH43DOYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu4YKus9AV13jXuqRKRtu4a5RP4I%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRV5JY5QGGBBDRPKM2LGH43DOYU.jpg&h=ccca2b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■前年9月22日，旺角警署外一度遭示威者包圍。"},{"pid":"a5e04908f11679db73c233aec3d83fb5d4d2640c","tid":2354013,"uid":171107,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5b45b746cb843234c2bb52d64c1e724b3970e915","tid":2354013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:29:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210105/KVSQGPMMZ5BLRDG45VWJRMPS7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FKVSQGPMMZ5BLRDG45VWJRMPS7Y%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=b11547ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210105%2FKVSQGPMMZ5BL